OL,3,CWarning from Devon man left paralysed
OL,4,Cin drink driving crash
OL,6,FNow he's sharing his story through ITV
OL,7,FNews West Country as a warning to
OL,8,Fothers, coinciding with Devon and
OL,9,FCornwall Police's annual Christmas
OL,10,FDrink Drive Campaign.
OL,12,FSeth said: "Don't make the wrong
OL,13,Fdecisions. If you're going out and
OL,14,Fgoing to be drinking, make sure you
OL,15,Fhave a designated driver. Making the
OL,16,Fwrong decision can change your life in
OL,17,Fseconds."
OL,19,FSeth said normally his friend would
OL,20,Fleave his car keys with bar stuff
OL,21,Funtil the following morning.
