OL,4,Cin drink driving crash
OL,6,FHe said: "We just didn't make that
OL,7,Fdecision that one night and now I've
OL,8,Fgot the rest of my life to pay for it."
OL,10,FAs part of the police campaign, there
OL,11,Fwill be increased patrols on the
OL,12,Fregion's roads over the festive season.
OL,14,FSergeant Owen Messenger, from the Road
OL,15,FCasualty Reduction team, said they
OL,16,Fhope an increased presence will remind
OL,17,Fpeople of the dangers of getting
OL,18,Fbehind the wheel.
