OL,6,FLast year there was a 38% increase in
OL,7,Fthe number of arrests for drink or
OL,8,Fdrug driving in Devon and Cornwall
OL,9,Fthroughout the campaign. Police say
OL,10,Fthat's because of those increased
OL,11,Fpatrols.
OL,13,FSgt Messenger said: "We will be out in
OL,14,Fmarked cars because we want people to
OL,15,Fknow that we are out there and that
OL,16,Fvisibility is key.
