OL,3,CWarning from Devon man left paralysed
OL,4,Cin drink driving crash
OL,6,F"Ultimately we want people not to
OL,7,Fcommit those offences of drink and
OL,8,Fdrug driving and we would rather not
OL,9,Fcatch anybody at all and nobody
OL,10,Fcommitted the offence than us to have
OL,11,Fto go out and either catch people or
OL,12,Fdeal with the consequences."
OL,14,FSeth spent 19 months in hospital and
OL,15,Fnow has a live-in carer 24 hours a day.
OL,17,FHis mum, Julie Marks, has recalled the
OL,18,Fmoment she walked into hospital and
OL,19,Flearned that her child would never be
OL,20,Fable to walk again.
