OL,3,CWarning from Devon man left paralysed
OL,4,Cin drink driving crash
OL,6,FShe said: "We went round some curtains
OL,7,Fand saw Seth lying on a bed,
OL,8,Fabsolutely out of it. Comatosed.
OL,9,FComing to every so often, with boards
OL,10,Fand drips and stands and anything and
OL,11,Feverything was everywhere and I just
OL,12,Flooked at him and I thought, he's
OL,13,Fbroken.
OL,15,F"You know, a consultant turns around
OL,16,Fand says to you 'he's never going to
OL,17,Fwalk again, he's probably not going to
OL,18,Fbe able to move his arms or anything
OL,19,Flike that' - your whole life changes.
