OL,6,F"And it's that ripple effect, people
OL,7,Fjust don't think about, that extra
OL,8,Fpint - 'oh yeah, I'll be fine'. But it
OL,9,Fonly takes that one pint. It's not
OL,10,Fworth it. It really isn't worth it.
OL,11,FYou might think you're fine but you're
OL,12,Fnot."
